room_title: Escape room "The Jungle" by Escape Games Live in York
review: The night started off with us meeting our host, Alex. He was a great host and answered any questions our group had right away. We did the Jungle escape room and it was awesome! I would highly recommend Escape Games Live for a group event. We will definitely be back to check out some other rooms.

room_title: Escape room "The Jungle" by Escape Games Live in York
review: Went today with three friends and our two daughters. It was a lot of fun! We did the Jungle room and Jonathan was there to help us out whenever we needed it. Did we make it out? Yep. In an hour? I'll never tell. I would definitely go back!
